        "text": "AUG. 12 1951? Daytime? NORTHERN NORWAY. 68°Latitude, 16° Longitude.\nAerial Object resembling a rocket guided missile, passed\nover 4 fishermen from direction of the Artic.\n#21 SOURCE: NY World Telegram and Sun Aug 15"
