        "text": "AUG. 20 1951? Monday Evening? LUBBOCK, Texas. 33°Lat., 102° Long.\nA group of glowing objects in an uneven crescent format-\nion, crossed sky at great speed, observed by the\nJournalism Professor of Texas Tech.\n#23 SOURCE: DALLAS Morning News Aug 27"
      },
      "translation": {
